title: Growing Yourself & The People Around You
itunes:title: Growing Yourself & The People Around You
description:
Just like a flower, we need the right circumstance to grow into who we can become, as do the people who we love that are around us. In this episode, we are going to talk about your environment to see if it is beneficial for you and the ones that you want to support in their growth.

 

Follow me on IG for more inspiration here: https://www.instagram.com/robdialjr/
